# Twilio Lookup API for Carrier and Caller Name
POST https://lookups.twilio.com/v2/PhoneNumbers/+2347077541387
Authorization: Basic {{base64_encoded_account_sid_and_auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": ["carrier", "caller-name"]
}

###

# Third-Party API for Name and Personal Info Verification
POST https://api.thirdparty.com/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{your_api_key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "+2347077541387"
}

###

# NumVerify API for Format, Location, and Carrier Info
GET https://apilayer.net/api/validate?access_key={{your_access_key}}&number=+2347077541387
Accept: application/json


# using my local API
POST http://localhost:3000/verify
Accept: application/json
